### =========================
### CREAR HOTELES
### =========================

### Crear hotel en Madrid
POST http://localhost:8080/api/hoteles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Hotel Palace",
  "ciudad": "Madrid",
  "categoria": 5
}

###

### Crear hotel en A Coruña
POST http://localhost:8080/api/hoteles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Hotel Atlántico",
  "ciudad": "A Coruña",
  "categoria": 4
}

###

### Crear hotel en Madrid 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/hoteles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Hotel Centro",
  "ciudad": "Madrid",
  "categoria": 3
}

###

### Crear hotel en Valencia
